Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NUh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...Don't mind them Kaya,\Nthis happens to me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the price of\Nbeing a famous adventurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just new recruits\Nwho heard about me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and came to join\Nthe Usopp pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not me. I came\Nhere to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor? From me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if\Nthere was any way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--you could help get us a boat.\N--[KLAHADORE] You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that this\Nis criminal trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThe weirdest guy ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango the hypnotist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually Klahadore,\Nthese people are--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me all about this\Nriff-raff after they've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now get out! All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave now, unless you have\Nsome business with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Do you think that you\Ncould help us get a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NCertainly not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAww...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NUsopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NCrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NYou have quite the reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are very well\Nknown in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NEh... He. He. Sure am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE] I hear you've\Nbeen on many an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite impressive for\Nsomeone as young as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, people who admire\Nme so much, call me Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's Captain Usopp to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NCaptain, huh? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father also had\Nsomething of a reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore, please just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never be anything more\Nthan the son of a filthy pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what sort of\Ntrouble you're up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ask is that\Nyou and your kind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,leave this respectable\Nyoung lady alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A filthy pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE] You and she are\Nfrom completely different worlds
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it money you're after?\NHow much do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cease this at once, Klahadore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe there is\Nany reason to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to this savage\Nyoung man, My Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NMy goal isn't to slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am merely stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I sympathize with\Nyour situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hate your\Ngreat, idiot of a father
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,for abandoning his\Nfamily and his village
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because of his mindless\Nlust for treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare insult\Nmy father ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--[USOPP grunts]\N--[KAYA gasps] Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you gotten\Nso worked up Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's times like these
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when you should do what\Nyou do best and lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about how your father\Nis really a traveling salesman,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or about how you aren't\Nreally related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE grunts]\NCase in point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He resorts to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the apple never falls\Nfar from the tree, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My father listened to his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and chose a life of\Nrisk and adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am proud to say\Nthat my old man
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, I have been known\Nto exaggerate from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will never lie\Nabout who my father is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to be ashamed\Nof my heritage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the son of a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, ONION whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE laughs] Pirates\Nare brave warriors of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,are they? [laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a twisted\Nway of putting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem\Nto understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you are living proof\Nof his savage blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You run around spouting lies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and use violence when\Nyou don't get your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To top it off,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you cozy up to the lady of\Nthe house to steal her fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I only--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're father is a\Nfilthy, no-good pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Treachery is in your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you would hatch\Nsuch an evil scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't let up, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it Usopp! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NNo more violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore isn't a bad person...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just trying to do what\Nhe thinks is best for me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes he goes too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grumbles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are never to\Ncome here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Ntell me twice, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last\Nyou'll ever see of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA whimpers]\NUsopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you butler jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Captain's not\Nthat kinda guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya stupid jerk-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, You don't have\Na bone to pick with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] What are you doing?\NDon't hide behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Let me go already!\NC'mon, Zoro! I'm Serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down! Put me down!\NI'm going to kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NYou will all leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA coughing, whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[door knocking, squeaking]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your meal is ready\Nnow, Miss Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NNo thank you, I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The cook would be most\Nupset to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He works his hardest,\Nday and night, to come up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,with delicious meals\Nthat suit your needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[silverware clinks]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NWhy were you so cruel to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I was wrong to talk\Nto Usopp without telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I will admit that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm very sorry for\Nnot being honest with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but this situation\Ndid not warrant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of harsh treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,May I sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE] It has\Nbeen quite some time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,since I first arrived\Nat this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon it will be three years
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have been in the\Nservice of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget\Nwhat happened
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,when I showed up at\Nyour father's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE] My former employers\Nwere brutal, pitiless men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd been kicked off\Nthe ship I worked on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for some small\Nblunder I had made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And with no work or money,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the verge of\Ndying like a beggar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KAYA gasps]\N--[GUARD A] Hey you, beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[GUARD B]\NGet outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the place\Nfor the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA gasps]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But, sir... He...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[GUARD A] Understood! Take\Nhim inside and tend to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NAs far as I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've died without\Nyour father's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe my life to your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that they're gone,\NI owe my life to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NI know that it isn't my place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to interfere with\Nyour friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have taken\Nsuch a bold step
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,unless I thought it\Nabsolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that Usopp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't exactly known for\Nhis upstanding character.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, If anything\Nwere to happen to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be my fault for\Nnot seeing to your safety
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would never be able to ask\Nforgiveness from your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think ill of me for my\Nchildish behavior earlier today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thankful to have you\Naround too, Klahadore,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I stand by my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp is one of the\Nnicest people I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NWe'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, he is still\Nnot welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore! You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\N"Blockhead" will do just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHey, Where'd Luffy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? He probably\Nran after that captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's at his secret spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, over by the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He always goes there when he's\Ngonna think something over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh? He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Luffy can\Ntake care of himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but where's your other friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, CARROT]\NOh yeah, Onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, he just\Nup and disappears a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And then he shows up\Noutta nowhere all freaked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION screaming]\NTerrible news, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NListen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Some nut job is on his way here\Nand he only walks backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER, CARROT]\NYou liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI, PEPPER, CARROT]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, which one of you people\Nhas the nerve to call me weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a normal guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,S'that so? You look insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NDon't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just an ordinary,\Nrun of the mill hypnotist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NA hypnotist? Really? Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NShow us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NYeah! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools, what makes you think\Nthat I would want to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,my masterful\Nhypnosis techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to a bunch of\Nroadside strangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOkay, you convinced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, watch the ring closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat a ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, by the count of "Jango,"\Nyou'll be in a deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOne...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS, JANGO snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWho is this freaky weirdo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI came here to be alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess that's\Nnot happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you follow me?\NWhat d'you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOh, ya know, nothin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOh...Ouch... [laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI can't believe that butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Insulting my old man like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah, I hate that guy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone says,\NYassop was a great pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always looked up to my\Nold man for living everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with his life on the line,\Nout in the open ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He made a brave choice\Nand I admire him for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that stupid,\Nsnotty butler
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,stomped all over my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know if you're ever\Ngonna see that girl again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]\NI don't know. Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll consider it if that\Nbutler apologizes to me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,for the things he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That butler right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That's the one, if he--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is\Nhe doing down here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhat's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jango.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I specifically ordered you to\Nkeep yourself inconspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean\Nsleeping in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax man, I've perfected\Nthe skills of the chameleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] There's someone else\Nwith him and, man, is he weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have all the necessary\Npreparations been made?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWe can start anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...on the "Rich\NGirl Murder Plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, USOPP gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NAh! Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NDon't call it murder, Jango.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like the sound of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOh right, accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an accident...\Nthat you planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what are those\Nguys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if we listen a little\Ncloser, we can find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NWe can't simply kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is critical to our plan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that Miss Kaya perishes in\Nan unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't screw that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically, on your signal,\Nthe men and I storm the village
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and manage to "accidentally"\Nkill the little rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you get her inheritance\Nand we all get paid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ignorance is astounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not related, so how could\NI inherit anything from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NYou'll work very hard to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NNo Jango, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen to me, this is\Nthe most important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you kill her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll use your hypnosis to\Nmake Kaya write her will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will say,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"I leave my entire fortune\Nto my butler, Klahadore".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, and only then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,will I have undisputed control\Nof her enormous fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And no one will suspect a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[KLAHADORE]\NI have spent three long years
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,gaining the trust of\Neveryone around me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it would be\Nunsurprising for her
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave the entirety of\Nher inheritance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Three years as\Na butler for this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure had us scared\Nback then, Captain Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you suddenly said you were\Ngiving up life as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In no time at all you set up\Nsomeone to be your double.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you let the world see\NCaptain Kuro get executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Only now, do I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that was just the\Nbeginning of this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the "Man of\Na Thousand Plans."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Never call me that again.\NI abandoned that name years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I now wish to obtain my wealth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,without attracting the\Nattention of the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\NI'm a pacifist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing] Some\Npacifist you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Murdering an entire family
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't exactly\Nqualify as peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I haven't\Nmurdered an entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The father's death\Nwasn't planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] Whatever you say,\Nit makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's all the same to you,\Nhurry up and give the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew is getting bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting in the waters\Nnear here for over a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the men are growing\Nmore anxious by the minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] This is horrible!\NThis is really horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it bad guy stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Weren't you\Nlistening to any of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys aren't\Njust bad, they're evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kuro is known\Nto be the most devious,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,scheming pirate around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And though he's\Nknown for his smarts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he's legendary for\Nhis brutality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Word had it that\Nthe Marines caught
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and executed him\Nthree years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but Captain Kuro\Nis alive and well,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,posing as Klahadore the butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's had his diabolical\Nsights set on Kaya's fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for the last three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] First, they'll\Nattack the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,then they'll kill Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] This is bad!\NThis is seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get down! They'll see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bad guys! You better\Nstay away from that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWho are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, they've spotted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry up and hide
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,before they decide you\Nneed a long slow death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, If it isn't Usopp,\Nthe mischievous town liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams] Oh, no!\NI'm spotted too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NDid you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Nope. Nothing at all.\NI don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't hear a peep.\NWe just got here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so we didn't hear\Nanything about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWell, If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NPay attention, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And watch this ring closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it? It's some\Nkind of weapon, we gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] By the count of "Jango,"\Nyou will be in a deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--One... Two...\N--[USOPP] Run for cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NJango!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--[USOPP whimpers] Heh?\N--[LUFFY snores]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--[JANGO snoring]\N--Jango, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see your still falling\Nasleep on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY snoring]\N--[USOPP] Hey be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He had to go and fall\Noff a cliff, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A pity really, I didn't\Nmean to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no way\Nhe could've survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThis can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really... dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWhat about the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything he could say\Nwould sound like, lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Jango,\Ntomorrow at daybreak,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the men are to\Nattack the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rough up the villagers some
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and tear up their homes\Na little, for good measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, make sure Miss\NKaya's death looks accidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just accept it Usopp. There\Nis nothing you can say or do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to warn the villagers of\Nthis impending tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP gasps, screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NAre you sure about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Of course I am,\Nmy plans are flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!\NI gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the village I\Ngrew up with is in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kaya's gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] I can't let that\Nhappen to the people I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] I'm Usopp,\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughs] I heard you've\Nbeen a little down lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd tell you\Na story to cheer you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] You would do well\Nto mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave or I'll call\Nsomeone who will make you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA laughs] And then?\NWhat happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI fought of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And bravely at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,First, for the giant cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I used what else but\Na giant cattail plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, KAYA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.34,0:23:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.11,0:24:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Usopp ran by\Nlooking pretty upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.83,0:24:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.17,0:24:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThat butler is a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.71,0:24:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He told his crew to\Nattack the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.79,0:24:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Well, now they'll\Nknow and they can run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.59,0:24:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Crisis averted right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.01,0:24:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.88,0:24:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.63,0:24:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWe need to stock up on food
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.97,0:24:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,before the meat shop\Nguy runs away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That's not the\Nissue at hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.18,0:24:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.93,0:24:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Expose the Plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.51,0:24:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Butler Captain Kuro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.68,0:24:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

